"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順個便寫埋食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個份量獨食岩岩好！<br />\n一人一份又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，自己單拖又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  &hellip;唔洗同人分就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n焗豬扒飯- 圖文食譜: <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/04/baked-pork-chop-with-fried-rice-oldlady.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F04%2Fbaked-pork-chop-with-fried-rice-oldlady.html%20&d=95vaTXnWF%2BaQOTHEBviKW7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=0ef1e5d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/04/baked-pork-chop-with-fried-rice-oldlady.html </a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=95vaTXnWF%2BaQOTHEBviKW7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=02302afd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=95vaTXnWF%2BaQOTHEBviKW7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=81f7d08a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=95vaTXnWF%2BaQOTHEBviKW7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=774865bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"7b9187575870a9b64e2790d811432bf0b94b49bf","tid":627661,"uid":116530,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:14:38.000Z",